steps.name: Click on the 'Companies' button from the sidebar menu
Click on the 'Clients' tab from the 'Companies' page
Click on the client name from the table
Click on the 'Contacts' tab from the company landing page
Click on the 'Client contacts' sub tab
Click on the 'Add contact' button from the 'Other contacts' sub tab
Click on the '+ Create contact' button from the 'Associate others to company' modal window
Enter email address for a new Rolodex user
Enter the First name for the Rolodex user
Enter the Last name for the Rolodex user
Enter the phone number for the Rolodex user
Click on the 'Permission template' dropdown field
Select the 'Collaborator' role from the 'Permission template' dropdown field
Click on the 'Finish' button to finish creating new Rolodex user
